{"tid":2020354,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"近半監警會委員屬再出發聯盟","createTime":"2020-05-17T04:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T04:28:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6a32feae55c8f36f5ecf1d23486af8a072df11cc","tid":2020354,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T04:08:22.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200517/2E45GKZZ54P6EKNS4T3K5F4H3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200517%2F2E45GKZZ54P6EKNS4T3K5F4H3U%2F&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e6196RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=77ff0684\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200517%2F2E45GKZZ54P6EKNS4T3K5F4H3U%2F&h=0b36b7f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200517/2E45GKZZ54P6EKNS4T3K5F4H3U/</a><br />\n<br />\n近半監警會委員屬再出發聯盟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200517/large/1589644416_4b48.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200517%2Flarge%2F1589644416_4b48.gif&h=8bb8670b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】監警報告淪為「撐警報告」，公眾都想知道，監警會成員是何方神聖？報告由秘書處專案組負責「釐清事實工作」，並由四名小組委員會主席組成督導委員會帶領，當中三人為「香港再出發大聯盟」共同發起人。三名副主席全為建制派立會議員及全國政協委員，而監警會中人亦多次發表令人譁然的撐警言論。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：稱速龍裝非制服 毋須展示編號<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n副主席謝偉銓屢撐警<br />\n<br />\n監警會現任副主席為謝偉銓、金融服務界張華峰及航運交通界易志明，謝及張去年已不。。。。。。。。。。。。，明顯有違主席梁定邦所稱需否作獨立調查監警會，法律上不容許監警會有立場的說法。<br />\n<br />\n督導委員會其中一名成員陳錦榮，曾組。。。。。。。。。。。。。。人大就《基本法》104條釋法，最終落敗。<br />\n<br />\n監警會委員全部由行政長官委任，截至今年年初共有26人。早於2016年年底監警。。。。。。。。。。。。。全國政協常委楊孫西之子楊華勇等，儼如變身「梁粉俱樂部」。<br />\n<br />\n去年新委任委員亦「承襲」特首身邊人系統，包括林鄭參選特首時競選辦資深顧問余黎青萍。<br />\n<br />\n比較監警會委員會名單，26人中近半人屬「香港再出發大聯盟」共同發起人，包括三名副主席張華峰、易志明、謝偉銓、成員鄭錦鐘、許宗盛、錢志庸、陳錦榮、藍德業、李家仁、楊華勇、李文斌、林定國。大聯盟由兩位未能完成兩屆任期的前特首董建華、梁振英任總召集人。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃翠儀"},{"pid":"b9c5c95003a9e1a35760b9f7b37a66cda63fe67b","tid":2020354,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T04:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KwZuaKq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKwZuaKq.gif&h=ae4bac16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca794dfaa7c8d1ec397e2486b9a3adace80706c4","tid":2020354,"uid":28432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T04:11:01.000Z","msg":"笑撚死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 張華鋒係監警會係咪訓住開會 唔怪得份報告咁高質"},{"pid":"0cd40a5d0141acf18e636c5fe55409f57e19ffe4","tid":2020354,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T04:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd7f01845f0f4f6881d43f1b0ce02a2c1e1b4a6","tid":2020354,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca794dfaa7c8d1ec397e2486b9a3adace80706c4","tid":2020354,"uid":28432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T04:11:01.000Z","msg":"笑撚死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 張華鋒係監警會係咪訓住開會 唔怪得份報告咁高質"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T04:28:46.000Z","msg":"有邊次唔撚瞓"}]}